<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Cyprus Amax is the fastest-growing and largest U.S.-owned mining company.  We are a leading worldwide producer of copper and coal, the world's largest producer of molybdenum and lithium, and hold a significant position in gold.  We are generating excitement in the mining industry through our combination of leading-edge technology, and a world of experience and know-how.  Our people are determined to make Cyprus Amax the most admired mining firm in the world.  We work hard to take a proactive environmental stance and have helped create Partners for Progress to work with local communities.  Cyprus Amax strives to sustain a high quality of life for our employees and our neighbors.">

