<FONT FACE="helvetica">
<B>Cyprus Amax</B> is the fastest-growing and largest U.S.-owned mining company.  We are a leading worldwide producer of <A HREF="about/copper.htm">copper</A>  and <A HREF="about/coal.htm">coal</A>, the world's largest producer of <A HREF="../madison/index.shtml">molybdenum</A> and <A HREF="about/lithium.htm">lithium</A>, and hold a significant position in <A HREF="about/gold.htm">gold</A>.  We are generating excitement in the mining industry through our combination of leading-edge technology, and a world of experience and know-how.  Our people are determined to make <B>Cyprus Amax</B> the most admired mining firm in the world.  We work hard to take a proactive environmental stance and have helped create <A HREF="partners/index.htm">Partners for Progress</A> to work with local communities.  <B>Cyprus Amax</B> strives to sustain a high quality of life for our employees and our neighbors.
